data.description: This 4 BR / 2 BA home is a must see and offers spacious living area with the primary bedroom on the 1st floor.  Eat-in-kitchen with stainless steel appliances, fresh paint, and LVP in main areas. Three large bedrooms are upstairs. All bathrooms have been updated, new HVAC 2023, newer water heater, roof replaced in 2016 and much more! Home is located on a corner lot with plenty of parking with 2-car garage and driveway. Close to The Farm amenities which feature a large zero entry pool, clubhouse, leisure trails, and playgrounds. This is a must see!
